         <div xml:id="alalal-ee1942"><!-- l3d1a6 -->
            <head xml:id="alalal-ee1942-Hd1e99">Articulus 6</head>
            <head xml:id="alalal-ee1942-Hd1e101" type="question-title">Quare tempus in quo misit Deus Fitium
suum, dicitur tempus plenitudinis,
tempus miserendi, annus benignitatis,
tempus gratia, etc.</head>
            <p xml:id="alalal-ee1942-d1e104">
               <lb ed="Bd" n="23"/>ARTICULUS VI.
<lb ed="Bd" n="24"/>Quare tempus in quo misit Deus Fitium
<lb ed="Bd" n="25"/>suum, dicitur tempus plenitudinis,
<lb ed="Bd" n="26"/>tempus miserendi, annus benignitatis,
<lb ed="Bd" n="27"/>tempus gratia, etc.
</p>
            <p xml:id="alalal-ee1942-d1e117">
               <lb ed="Bd" n="28"/>Deinde quaeritur de hoc quod dicit,
<lb ed="Bd" n="29"/>ibi, A, circa medium: <quote xml:id="alalal-ee1942-Qd1e123"> Annus 
benigni<lb break="no" ed="Bd" n="30"/>A)</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="alalal-ee1942-d1e129">
               <lb ed="Bd" n="31"/>Que est enim ratio quatuor vel trium
<lb ed="Bd" n="32"/>nominum hujus temporis, scilicet, ut
<lb ed="Bd" n="33"/>dicatur tempus plenitudinis, tempus 
mi<lb break="no" ed="Bd" n="34"/>serendi, tempus benignitatis, et tempus
<lb ed="Bd" n="35"/>gratiae ?
</p>
            <p xml:id="alalal-ee1942-d1e143">
               <lb ed="Bd" n="36"/>Ad hoc dicendum, quod ratio dicta
<lb ed="Bd" n="37"/>est, quare dicitur tempus plenitudinis.
<lb ed="Bd" n="38"/>Quod vero ex plenitudine sequebatur 
red<lb break="no" ed="Bd" n="39"/>emptio miserorum, ideo dicitur tempus
<cb ed="#Bd" n="b"/>
               <lb ed="Bd" n="40"/>miserendi, Osee, xt,8: Conturbata est
<lb ed="Bd" n="41"/>penitudo mea. Et, Jerem. xxx1,3: <quote xml:id="alalal-ee1942-Qd1e160">In
<lb ed="Bd" n="42"/>charttate perpetua dilest te: ideo 
allra<lb break="no" ed="Bd" n="43"/>ai te, miserans</quote>. Ad juvamen autem 
tan<lb break="no" ed="Bd" n="44"/>tum exigebatur ignila bonitas, quae 
li<lb break="no" ed="Bd" n="45"/>quefaciens bonum intus in omnes effluere
<lb ed="Bd" n="46"/>faceret : et ideo dicitur annus 
benignita<lb break="no" ed="Bd" n="47"/>tis. Cantic. 1, 3: <quote xml:id="alalal-ee1942-Qd1e176">Oleum effusum nomen
<lb ed="Bd" n="48"/>tuum: ideo adolescentule dilexerunt te
<lb ed="Bd" n="49"/>nimis. Tempus autem gratie</quote> dicitur
<lb ed="Bd" n="50"/>propter copiam gratia ad mandata 
im<lb break="no" ed="Bd" n="51"/>plenda.
</p>
